I’ll use formulas so the sheet remains dynamic:
- Bn: `=IF(A n =0,0,IF(A n >0,A n /MAX($A$2:$A$16)*5,A n /ABS(MIN($A$2:$A$16))*5))`
- Cn: `=RANK(B n ,$B$2:$B$16,0)`

